            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgMA\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgMA', '0%')\" src=\"images/Mapswire/mapswire-continent_na-printable-map-north-america-robinson-269_mesoamerica2.jpg\" class=\"imgcenter\"/>Figura 1: Mapa de Mesoamérica de acordo com os estudos de Cremear (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('2d720f02-051c-4469-b425-7d020f2c2f9b'); return false;\">Creamer, W., pp. 37 - 55, <htdate0></a>)</p>",
